{"thag2.45:0.1":"Theragatha 2.45 ","thag2.45:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.45:0.3":"Pancamavagga ","thag2.45:0.4":"Visakhapancalaputtattheragatha ","thag2.45:1.1":"“Na ukkhipe no ca parikkhipe pare, ","thag2.45:1.2":"Na okkhipe paragatam na eraye; ","thag2.45:1.3":"Na cattavannam parisasu byahare, ","thag2.45:1.4":"Anuddhato sammitabhani subbato. ","thag2.45:2.1":"Susukhumanipunatthadassina, ","thag2.45:2.2":"Matikusalena nivatavuttina; ","thag2.45:2.3":"Samsevitavuddhasilina, ","thag2.45:2.4":"Nibbanam na hi tena dullabhan”ti. ","thag2.45:2.5":"… Visakho pancalaputto thero …. "}